[http://www.shipbrook.com/jeff/CoS/narconon/osb1992.html Findings of Fact regarding the Narconon-Chilocco Application For Certification by the Board of Mental Health, State of Oklahoma] {{Wayback|url=http://www.shipbrook.com/jeff/CoS/narconon/osb1992.html |date=20060614102514 }}, 13 December 1991 (hosted by [[David_Touretzky|David Touretzky]])
